--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README - TORIC/CQL3D IPS Iterative Solver
AUTHOR - SAM FRANK - frank@psfc.mit.edu
DATE   - 10/2022
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This folder contains the IPS setup for the TORIC/CQL3D iterative solver for a
single minority species. This case is based on the the ITER-He3 minority heating
simulation in Lee et. al. Phys. Plasmas. 24, 052502 (2017), but the underlying
code has recieved a number of updates.
